1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:03,520
笙ｪShrugging off past burdens笙ｪ

2
00:00:03,520 --> 00:00:06,110
笙ｪBeneath the mask, who am I?笙ｪ

3
00:00:06,780 --> 00:00:10,180
笙ｪRelease and find wider shores笙ｪ

4
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:14,890
笙ｪLove's a riddle, and rain pours heavy笙ｪ

5
00:00:15,260 --> 00:00:17,790
笙ｪCrossed paths, now downward fall笙ｪ

6
00:00:18,130 --> 00:00:21,570
笙ｪFrom dust arises starlight's spark笙ｪ

7
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:28,540
笙ｪTearing through
the night's dense blockade笙ｪ

8
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:34,300
笙ｪHeart's flame illuminates all solitude笙ｪ

9
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:37,590
笙ｪLet time's sails drift endlessly笙ｪ

10
00:00:37,590 --> 00:00:40,200
笙ｪThrough wandering exile笙ｪ

11
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:47,980
笙ｪBreaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew笙ｪ

12
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:51,710
笙ｪMoon as song, life as flame笙ｪ

13
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:54,610
笙ｪNameless heart clings fiercely笙ｪ

14
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:55,930
笙ｪLet me笙ｪ

15
00:00:56,120 --> 00:01:00,200
笙ｪCharge toward the next raging river笙ｪ

16
00:01:00,650 --> 00:01:03,330
笙ｪMoon darts, snow falls笙ｪ

17
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,320
笙ｪWe tread rugged paths to reunite笙ｪ

18
00:01:06,490 --> 00:01:07,960
笙ｪHands held tight笙ｪ

19
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:12,130
笙ｪWe forever live for love's sake笙ｪ

20
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:22,740
笙ｪShadow's spear burns fiercely笙ｪ

21
00:01:24,170 --> 00:01:29,720
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,900
=Episode 22=

23
00:01:33,110 --> 00:01:33,729
Gentlemen,

24
00:01:34,030 --> 00:01:35,150
fate brought us together

25
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:36,190
at the academy.

26
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:37,870
Why don't you talk things through?

27
00:01:37,990 --> 00:01:38,550
Cheng Lisu,

28
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:39,990
you may not know.

29
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,390
There is no misunderstanding

30
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:45,350
between us.

31
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:48,710
Right.

32
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:50,190
No misunderstandings.

33
00:01:50,990 --> 00:01:51,750
In the end,

34
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:53,430
I'm nothing

35
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:55,030
but an oath-breaker.

36
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:12,550
Look!

37
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:22,690
(Hua Youxian)

38
00:02:40,510 --> 00:02:41,390
Hua Youxian?

39
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:43,310
She was

40
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,390
the top of the Ruyun House,

41
00:02:44,670 --> 00:02:45,630
unmatched in Yaojing.

42
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:47,990
How could she end up in Chonghuai?

43
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:08,310
Bravo!

44
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,150
Great!

45
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:11,870
You are

46
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,790
gracefully charming.

47
00:03:13,390 --> 00:03:14,550
You truly deserve

48
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,910
the Ruyun House's reputation.

49
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:18,190
Your heavenly voice

50
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:19,470
lives up to its fame.

51
00:03:20,110 --> 00:03:20,870
Our money

52
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,310
was well spent indeed.

53
00:04:01,350 --> 00:04:02,230
Years have passed.

54
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:03,310
How have you been?

55
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:04,540
All is well.

56
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:05,390
Miss Hua,

57
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:06,110
and you?

58
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,070
I'm well, too.

59
00:04:07,830 --> 00:04:08,590
Speaking of which,

60
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:10,070
I share a special connection

61
00:04:10,110 --> 00:04:10,950
with you all.

62
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:12,070
Back then,

63
00:04:12,550 --> 00:04:13,590
I received

64
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,350
a love letter from one of you.

65
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:19,149
Certain people
always chase after beauties.

66
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:20,750
It must be his work.

67
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,390
Back then, I ranked

68
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,110
second to last at Xianchang Academy.

69
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:25,030
I couldn't even

70
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:26,150
write proper essays,

71
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,790
let alone love letters.

72
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:30,270
To prove your innocence to Miss Song,

73
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,510
you're exposing this.

74
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:33,950
Huaijin excels in

75
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,390
arts and martial skills.

76
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,030
He always ranked first

77
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,230
at the academy.

78
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:39,430
I bet this letter

79
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:40,430
was his doing.

80
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,190
See? He's not denying it.

81
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:43,830
It's a yes.

82
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,070
A penalty drink.

83
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:46,110
Definitely him.

84
00:04:46,670 --> 00:04:48,510
Who knew you would

85
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:49,950
have such a romantic side?

86
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:56,070
General Fengyun, since you are here,

87
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:58,110
as the local magistrate,

88
00:04:58,550 --> 00:04:59,510
I should host you.

89
00:05:00,550 --> 00:05:01,830
Tomorrow, I'll prepare a banquet

90
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:03,790
and hope you'll come.

91
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:09,310
It's rare for me to come.

92
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,030
Miss Hua, would you like

93
00:05:11,590 --> 00:05:12,470
to drink with me?

94
00:05:20,910 --> 00:05:21,950
Of course,

95
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,550
I would like to.

96
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,510
Mr. Yang,

97
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,590
why the long face?

98
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,710
Speaking of which,

99
00:06:07,030 --> 00:06:07,910
Miss Hua,

100
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:09,510
what brought you to Chonghuai?

101
00:06:12,710 --> 00:06:13,910
I met a gentleman.

102
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:15,870
Believing him

103
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,230
to be

104
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,470
my lifelong partner.

105
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:20,150
I bought my freedom

106
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,270
and married him.

107
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:23,830
So

108
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,630
you are married?

109
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:27,750
Yes.

110
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,270
But

111
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:32,550
my judgment failed me.

112
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:33,790
Eventually,

113
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,070
we divorced.

114
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,870
Why the separation?

115
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,670
I entrusted myself

116
00:06:43,909 --> 00:06:44,670
to the wrong man.

117
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:46,830
You were

118
00:06:46,909 --> 00:06:48,150
once renowned across the land.

119
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,230
I heard of your legendary fame, too.

120
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,150
Choosing marriage at your career's peak

121
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:54,750
meant you held

122
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:55,750
deep affection for him.

123
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:02,550
When I left the Ruyun House, the madam

124
00:07:03,030 --> 00:07:03,710
asked me,

125
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:06,710
"Have you ever seen a moth fly

126
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,950
into a flame and end well?"

127
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:10,510
I was young then

128
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,070
and firmly believed

129
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,590
that even a fleeting moment

130
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,590
of warmth would be worth chasing.

131
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:17,950
I naturally fell for him

132
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:19,230
and left with him

133
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,110
without hesitation.

134
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:22,950
Later,

135
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,190
our affection dissipated,

136
00:07:27,150 --> 00:07:28,270
so I left him.

137
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:29,990
Isn't that human nature?

138
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:37,550
Now,

139
00:07:37,909 --> 00:07:38,990
I live freely

140
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:39,750
in this city,

141
00:07:40,030 --> 00:07:41,750
self-sufficient and unbound.

142
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:42,950
So joyful.

143
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,430
I've never regretted

144
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,870
any decision I've made,

145
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:49,350
be it past or present.

146
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,750
Your clarity of purpose

147
00:07:53,350 --> 00:07:54,430
is admirable.

148
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,150
Let me toast to you.

149
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:02,870
Thank you,

150
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,190
Miss.

151
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:08,750
You have sharp eyes.

152
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:19,150
Your dance is captivating

153
00:08:19,710 --> 00:08:20,550
and famous.

154
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,310
Now, you're single.

155
00:08:23,110 --> 00:08:23,870
Our garrison has

156
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:25,030
many outstanding young men.

157
00:08:25,670 --> 00:08:26,230
Perhaps

158
00:08:26,710 --> 00:08:28,150
some might suit your standards?

159
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,710
Your brave warriors

160
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:35,030
are certainly worthy of me.

161
00:08:38,429 --> 00:08:39,030
Xiao Jue.

162
00:08:40,070 --> 00:08:40,830
What do you mean?

163
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:42,510
(He's egging him on.)

164
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:44,270
Both are unwed.

165
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:45,670
Why not play

166
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,270
the matchmaker?

167
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:53,670
It's my marriage.

168
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,150
None of your concern.

169
00:08:56,110 --> 00:08:56,710
I...

170
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:58,230
I...

171
00:09:02,990 --> 00:09:04,630
Miss Hua is beautiful and skilled in

172
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:05,470
song and dance.

173
00:09:05,950 --> 00:09:06,590
She deserves

174
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:08,110
a promising young partner.

175
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,590
Why do you object?

176
00:09:10,110 --> 00:09:10,830
Exactly. Huaijin.

177
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:12,070
Go introduce her

178
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:12,790
to some brave ones

179
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,750
of your men.

180
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,350
Naturally.

181
00:09:18,070 --> 00:09:18,950
Xiao Jue.

182
00:09:25,470 --> 00:09:26,030
Youxian.

183
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:28,350
The love letter

184
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:29,950
was from you, right?

185
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:32,990
Her ex-husband

186
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:34,390
is also you.

187
00:09:34,830 --> 00:09:36,230
So it was you all along.

188
00:09:39,590 --> 00:09:40,190
Back then,

189
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,950
we were both young.

190
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:54,110
I want to buy your freedom.

191
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:56,030
I wonder

192
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:57,670
if you would like

193
00:09:58,790 --> 00:10:00,110
to become my wife?

194
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,790
Our backgrounds are worlds apart.

195
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:15,150
Marriage isn't a game.

196
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,670
There's too much at stake.

197
00:10:19,190 --> 00:10:20,110
Let me think again.

198
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:21,710
Stop right there!

199
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:26,230
Dreaming of marrying a courtesan?

200
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:28,070
You'll disgrace our family!

201
00:10:28,990 --> 00:10:31,110
Defending a traitor against your father?

202
00:10:31,430 --> 00:10:32,390
Leave now,

203
00:10:32,630 --> 00:10:34,310
and you're no longer a Yang!

204
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:36,230
Don't come back ever!

205
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,990
Why torture yourself?

206
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,310
Come away with me.

207
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:05,110
Alright.

208
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:06,910
I'll go with you.

209
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:13,760
(Yang Mansion)

210
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:18,230
I'm worthless.

211
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:22,710
Tell me.

212
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:24,990
What's truly burdening you?

213
00:11:28,070 --> 00:11:28,750
Tell me!

214
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:38,550
Give back my wine.

215
00:11:47,950 --> 00:11:48,590
Enough.

216
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,630
Let's divorce.

217
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:55,830
May we

218
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:57,630
never meet again.

219
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,430
I'm unworthy.

220
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:10,110
Mingzhi,

221
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,110
how could you be so blind?

222
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:14,710
You never compromised your will

223
00:12:15,590 --> 00:12:16,390
or dignity.

224
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:18,910
So free-spirited and open-hearted.

225
00:12:19,350 --> 00:12:20,590
Truly admirable.

226
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:23,150
You should be our role model as women.

227
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:25,430
I'm flattered.

228
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:26,990
Life is too short

229
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:28,670
to waste on self-compromise.

230
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:35,630
Youxian.

231
00:12:37,950 --> 00:12:38,590
You...

232
00:12:40,110 --> 00:12:41,030
failed the Commander

233
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,830
and then Miss Hua.

234
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:45,270
A blind and foolish man.

235
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:48,230
I was thinking

236
00:12:51,190 --> 00:12:52,270
back then, the Commander

237
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:54,510
lost both parents,

238
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,310
his comrades fell in battle,

239
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,230
and his friend betrayed him.

240
00:12:58,750 --> 00:13:00,070
Knowing something was wrong

241
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:01,630
but finding no proof.

242
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:04,270
That feeling of helplessness

243
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,590
must have been unbearable.

244
00:13:11,070 --> 00:13:12,110
As for Miss Hua,

245
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:13,910
who became your wife,

246
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:16,870
she deserved your respect,

247
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:21,430
but you neglected her.

248
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:23,310
Did you think

249
00:13:23,830 --> 00:13:24,550
avoiding violence

250
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:25,710
meant keeping

251
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:26,870
your gentleman's code?

252
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:28,670
Don't you know

253
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:31,230
complete indifference and neglect

254
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,790
hurt more than blows?

255
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:34,750
It means

256
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,350
from your heart

257
00:13:37,310 --> 00:13:38,350
to your eyes,

258
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:41,230
she ceased to exist.

259
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,710
My father's wrongful conviction

260
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:56,510
has nothing to do with you.

261
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,030
I never expected

262
00:13:59,710 --> 00:14:00,430
your single word

263
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:02,150
to change everything.

264
00:14:03,190 --> 00:14:04,230
I did resent you

265
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:06,790
for your disrespectful remarks,

266
00:14:08,150 --> 00:14:09,150
but that's in the past.

267
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,190
We're but specks

268
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:12,750
in the vast river of time,

269
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,310
gone in an instant.

270
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,030
I won't lecture you,

271
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,150
nor should you trap yourself.

272
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:24,910
When you're at rock bottom,

273
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,230
every step taken

274
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:29,910
is upward progress.

275
00:14:31,030 --> 00:14:32,710
Escapism and despair achieve nothing.

276
00:14:33,790 --> 00:14:35,030
I'll find the truth to clear

277
00:14:35,950 --> 00:14:36,790
my father's name

278
00:14:37,950 --> 00:14:38,950
and restore honor

279
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:41,990
to the Xiao Army.

280
00:14:43,830 --> 00:14:44,870
That day will come.

281
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:50,790
As for Miss Hua,

282
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,150
rather than feeling guilty,

283
00:14:53,950 --> 00:14:54,830
take action instead.

284
00:14:56,070 --> 00:14:56,990
Self-pity

285
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:58,990
is utterly useless.

286
00:15:06,190 --> 00:15:07,070
Stop drinking.

287
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:07,870
You'll be drunk.

288
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:11,470
Do you have troubles, Miss?

289
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:20,750
I made a righteous lecture earlier,

290
00:15:22,590 --> 00:15:24,910
but I'm just a deserter myself.

291
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:27,110
What right do I have

292
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:28,950
to criticize Yang Mingzhi?

293
00:15:30,990 --> 00:15:32,750
How ridiculous.

294
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:36,670
You must have

295
00:15:38,070 --> 00:15:39,230
your own struggles, too.

296
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:48,870
My minor troubles

297
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,790
pale compared to his suffering.

298
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,470
They're insignificant.

299
00:15:56,990 --> 00:15:59,350
But I see your pain.

300
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:20,510
Youxian.

301
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:33,030
I was wrong.

302
00:16:34,590 --> 00:16:35,990
I won't ask your forgiveness.

303
00:16:36,830 --> 00:16:37,590
I just wish

304
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,350
to return to your side.

305
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:43,830
If possible,

306
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:45,310
I want to make up

307
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:46,270
for the hurt I caused.

308
00:16:48,190 --> 00:16:48,870
It is

309
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:51,670
none of my concern.

310
00:16:53,830 --> 00:16:54,390
Youxian.

311
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:01,870
Youxian.

312
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:03,310
That's my only wish.

313
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,150
You can ignore me,

314
00:17:05,829 --> 00:17:06,470
reject me,

315
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:08,869
but I want to stay with you

316
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:13,829
because I truly love you.

317
00:17:44,910 --> 00:17:45,710
Actually...

318
00:17:48,430 --> 00:17:50,030
Actually, I...

319
00:17:54,390 --> 00:17:56,110
How much did you drink tonight?

320
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,150
Will you hate me?

321
00:18:09,230 --> 00:18:09,790
Commander.

322
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:13,270
Commander.

323
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:17,670
He Yan let me

324
00:18:17,710 --> 00:18:19,030
deliver this letter to you.

325
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:25,910
(By the riverside pavilion,
awaiting our conversation.)

326
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,110
(I'll be waiting.)

327
00:18:27,430 --> 00:18:28,910
You see each other every day.

328
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:30,390
Why write letters instead of

329
00:18:30,790 --> 00:18:31,510
speaking directly?

330
00:18:38,910 --> 00:18:39,630
Mr. Xiao.

331
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:43,550
Miss Hua.

332
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:46,470
I came here

333
00:18:46,470 --> 00:18:47,750
to thank you.

334
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:48,790
Why?

335
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:50,190
You went to great trouble

336
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:51,070
to help

337
00:18:51,190 --> 00:18:52,070
Yang Mingzhi and me.

338
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:54,510
I'm deeply grateful.

339
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:58,230
I wanted to beat him up,

340
00:18:58,830 --> 00:19:00,790
but the opportunity slipped away.

341
00:19:03,150 --> 00:19:05,030
So you're blaming me, Mr. Xiao?

342
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:07,790
His choice to be with me

343
00:19:07,870 --> 00:19:08,550
is his freedom.

344
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:10,230
And how I choose to respond

345
00:19:10,550 --> 00:19:11,350
is mine.

346
00:19:11,870 --> 00:19:12,470
Good then.

347
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:13,910
I'm sorry.

348
00:19:14,510 --> 00:19:15,190
I have to go.

349
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:17,500
By the way,

350
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:20,110
someone came with you to Ruyun House

351
00:19:20,390 --> 00:19:21,510
back then too.

352
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,390
I remember very clearly.

353
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,110
Delicate yet determined,

354
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:26,230
wearing a mask,

355
00:19:26,670 --> 00:19:27,950
refusing to reveal the identity.

356
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:29,990
Where is the person now?

357
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:32,790
All things pass away.

358
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:34,990
Not worth mentioning.

359
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:39,390
So,

360
00:19:39,630 --> 00:19:41,670
you two have grown distant?

361
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:43,870
Right.

362
00:19:44,150 --> 00:19:45,950
You've been battling everywhere.

363
00:19:46,430 --> 00:19:47,230
It must've been hard

364
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,270
for you to stay in touch.

365
00:19:49,230 --> 00:19:50,830
After all, she's a lady.

366
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:56,070
What?

367
00:19:59,870 --> 00:20:01,310
Don't you know, Mr. Xiao?

368
00:20:01,630 --> 00:20:03,390
She wore a chest binder

369
00:20:04,150 --> 00:20:05,190
and acted so nervous.

370
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:06,830
When I casually teased her,

371
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:08,110
she became flustered.

372
00:20:08,470 --> 00:20:10,710
That shy, nervous demeanor
could only belong

373
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:11,950
to a young lady.

374
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:13,590
My eyes never deceive me.

375
00:20:15,890 --> 00:20:20,190
(Yunlai Inn)

376
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:21,190
Strangely enough,

377
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:22,870
He Rufei's sister

378
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,950
is also called

379
00:20:24,990 --> 00:20:25,790
He Yan.

380
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:30,350
A woman like you

381
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:33,390
joined Yezhou Garrison as a new recruit.

382
00:20:34,190 --> 00:20:35,590
There must be a hidden story.

383
00:20:36,470 --> 00:20:37,350
The day will come

384
00:20:38,630 --> 00:20:40,030
when your secrets are uncovered.

385
00:20:40,910 --> 00:20:42,270
What secrets could I have?

386
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,030
We were simply

387
00:20:44,950 --> 00:20:46,150
meant to meet each other.

388
00:20:49,110 --> 00:20:50,550
Beware of He Rufei.

389
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:52,910
He made me hold back

390
00:20:52,950 --> 00:20:54,510
General Xiao's plea for help

391
00:20:55,390 --> 00:20:56,790
for a few days.

392
00:20:57,430 --> 00:20:58,390
Beware of whom?

393
00:21:01,630 --> 00:21:02,590
(Who are you really?)

394
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:05,190
(Miss He Yan from the He family?)

395
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:06,590
(Or He Rufei, the one)

396
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:08,230
(from back then who was afraid)

397
00:21:09,430 --> 00:21:10,430
(to show his true face?)

398
00:21:12,190 --> 00:21:13,390
(If you're He Rufei,)

399
00:21:14,150 --> 00:21:15,670
(then who is the current He Rufei?)

400
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,950
(If you're the He Rufei of old,)

401
00:21:18,070 --> 00:21:18,790
(why would you)

402
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:20,710
(abandon us in our direst hour?)

403
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:33,820
Commander.

404
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:42,710
You do know the Xiao's sword techniques.

405
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:44,030
You've found out.

406
00:22:44,510 --> 00:22:45,710
The Qinglang Sword Style

407
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:47,310
is known by the Xiaos

408
00:22:48,230 --> 00:22:49,590
and one other person only.

409
00:22:52,990 --> 00:22:53,550
Exactly.

410
00:22:55,950 --> 00:22:57,270
I was once He Rufei.

411
00:22:58,630 --> 00:22:59,710
That's not my true name.

412
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:01,710
I am He Yan,

413
00:23:02,750 --> 00:23:03,510
the stepsister

414
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:04,590
of the current He Rufei.

415
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:06,710
From childhood,

416
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:08,990
our identities were swapped.

417
00:23:09,870 --> 00:23:10,870
You exchanged identities?

418
00:23:11,630 --> 00:23:12,510
I've been He Rufei

419
00:23:12,950 --> 00:23:14,190
for as long as I can remember.

420
00:23:14,790 --> 00:23:15,390
They claimed

421
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:17,190
my brother wouldn't live long.

422
00:23:17,830 --> 00:23:19,230
I had to impersonate He Rufei,

423
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:21,230
or the family's noble title

424
00:23:21,710 --> 00:23:22,670
would be revoked.

425
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:25,190
So I had no choice

426
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:26,630
but to live as He Rufei.

427
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:29,150
But I refused to submit to

428
00:23:29,190 --> 00:23:29,910
such a fate.

429
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,510
So I left home and joined

430
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:32,990
the Fuyue Army.

431
00:23:33,870 --> 00:23:34,710
I earned merits

432
00:23:35,390 --> 00:23:36,230
and received honors,

433
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,990
but my brother who should've died young

434
00:23:40,390 --> 00:23:41,550
was still alive.

435
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:43,790
When he returned home,

436
00:23:45,470 --> 00:23:46,710
he poisoned and blinded me.

437
00:23:48,150 --> 00:23:50,190
Then he stole General Feihong's identity

438
00:23:51,390 --> 00:23:53,110
and even tried to kill me.

439
00:23:58,230 --> 00:23:59,430
Perhaps God

440
00:24:00,430 --> 00:24:01,550
took pity on me,

441
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:03,830
giving me another chance at life.

442
00:24:05,150 --> 00:24:06,710
That's how He Yan came to be.

443
00:24:07,710 --> 00:24:08,710
I am He Yan,

444
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:10,270
but also He Rufei.

445
00:24:11,630 --> 00:24:13,270
I told you I wanted to earn glory.

446
00:24:13,950 --> 00:24:14,710
That wasn't a lie.

447
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,430
Because I have to

448
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:18,030
rise to his level

449
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:19,070
to expose his lies

450
00:24:20,630 --> 00:24:22,110
and prevent him

451
00:24:23,710 --> 00:24:24,590
from harming

452
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:25,710
more innocent people.

453
00:24:27,710 --> 00:24:28,830
Anything that belongs to me,

454
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:31,670
I will reclaim personally.

455
00:24:36,390 --> 00:24:37,390
Xiao Jue, sorry

456
00:24:38,710 --> 00:24:39,710
for keeping it from you.

457
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:41,990
I just didn't know

458
00:24:42,910 --> 00:24:43,990
how to face you.

459
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:44,870
Only a question.

460
00:24:45,630 --> 00:24:46,630
In the Mingshui Battle,

461
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:49,070
was it you who delayed

462
00:24:50,790 --> 00:24:51,750
the reinforcements?

463
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:58,310
Yes.

464
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,230
I sent

465
00:25:01,030 --> 00:25:02,510
late reinforcements...

466
00:25:03,230 --> 00:25:04,710
30,000 Xiao Army soldiers died,

467
00:25:06,150 --> 00:25:07,790
and my parents died one after another.

468
00:25:08,510 --> 00:25:10,150
There's a conspiracy in the battle. I...

469
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:11,430
After lying to me for so long,

470
00:25:12,310 --> 00:25:13,190
how can you expect me

471
00:25:13,230 --> 00:25:14,990
to believe your one-sided claims?

472
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:22,030
You're right.

473
00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:24,630
I deceived you.

474
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,630
How could I demand

475
00:25:27,350 --> 00:25:28,870
your immediate trust?

476
00:25:33,990 --> 00:25:35,630
But I will find evidence

477
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:37,630
to uncover the truth.

478
00:25:43,030 --> 00:25:44,590
If you don't want to see me again,

479
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:48,150
I'll leave.

480
00:25:52,990 --> 00:25:57,150
笙ｪPerhaps I'll regret saying goodbye笙ｪ

481
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:05,310
笙ｪMaybe we can't share sorrows and joys笙ｪ

482
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:05,820
Commander,

483
00:26:06,390 --> 00:26:07,170
if you don't do it,

484
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:07,990
let me kill her!

485
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:10,370
Commander,

486
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:11,750
she killed so many.

487
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:13,230
How can we let her go?

488
00:26:13,830 --> 00:26:14,870
Letting her walk free

489
00:26:15,870 --> 00:26:16,790
is too merciful.

490
00:26:20,610 --> 00:26:25,670
笙ｪBefore fate is confirmed笙ｪ

491
00:26:25,670 --> 00:26:27,150
You will stay in Yezhou Garrison.

492
00:26:28,150 --> 00:26:29,150
You can't leave there

493
00:26:30,230 --> 00:26:31,510
until the truth is uncovered.

494
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:37,890
笙ｪLifelong devotion turns into a vow笙ｪ

495
00:26:38,050 --> 00:26:41,270
笙ｪThat's my last wish笙ｪ

496
00:26:42,180 --> 00:26:48,020
笙ｪAwaiting the spread of moonlight笙ｪ

497
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,910
How about...?

498
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:25,350
- Commander.
- Commander.

499
00:27:26,870 --> 00:27:27,390
We're here.

500
00:28:06,630 --> 00:28:07,150
(Today,)

501
00:28:07,710 --> 00:28:08,310
you can

502
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:09,510
do everything you wish to do

503
00:28:10,190 --> 00:28:11,150
without worries.

504
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,390
Just be your true self

505
00:28:13,870 --> 00:28:14,870
as you've always been.

506
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:16,470
Whatever you like

507
00:28:17,230 --> 00:28:17,990
and dislike,

508
00:28:18,870 --> 00:28:19,590
(say it outright.)

509
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:21,310
(Cheer yourself up.)

510
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:22,830
(Can I truly)

511
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:24,870
do whatever I want?

512
00:28:26,150 --> 00:28:26,910
Do as you please.

513
00:28:30,390 --> 00:28:30,950
Okay.

514
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:32,390
Do as I please.

515
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:42,050
笙ｪWhat is there to fear?
We'll move forward together笙ｪ

516
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:49,280
笙ｪThrough endless dawns and dusks,
to eternity笙ｪ

517
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:53,490
笙ｪAwaiting the crescent moon's
reflection in your heart笙ｪ

518
00:28:53,890 --> 00:28:56,410
笙ｪSplendor fades from your eyes笙ｪ

519
00:28:56,830 --> 00:29:00,870
笙ｪCrimson threads entwine like rings,
binding our first vow笙ｪ

520
00:29:00,870 --> 00:29:01,710
(Only a hundred.)

521
00:29:02,390 --> 00:29:03,590
(As long as it pleases you,)

522
00:29:04,550 --> 00:29:05,310
(it's worth it.)

523
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:12,290
笙ｪZither and harp
accompany our dancing dreams笙ｪ

524
00:29:12,610 --> 00:29:15,270
笙ｪThe brocade moon writes our vow,
keeping this promise笙ｪ

525
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:16,150
Does it look good?

526
00:29:17,230 --> 00:29:17,910
Yeah.

527
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:23,040
笙ｪAwaiting the crescent moon's
reflection in your heart笙ｪ

528
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:25,970
笙ｪSplendor fades from your eyes笙ｪ

529
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:33,430
笙ｪCrimson threads entwine like rings,
binding our first vow笙ｪ

530
00:29:33,430 --> 00:29:37,820
笙ｪTime lingers as you and I share
overlapping palm lines笙ｪ

531
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:41,840
笙ｪZither and harp
accompany our dancing dreams笙ｪ

532
00:29:42,170 --> 00:29:48,700
笙ｪThe brocade moon writes our vow,
keeping this promise笙ｪ

533
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:07,470
My bottom.

534
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:11,470
You really did it!

535
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:12,640
Wang Ba.

536
00:30:12,910 --> 00:30:13,950
Can you smell meat?

537
00:30:16,630 --> 00:30:17,390
Oh, really.

538
00:30:17,630 --> 00:30:18,790
No, stop. Stop fighting.

539
00:30:19,070 --> 00:30:20,750
I didn't eat lunch.

540
00:30:21,590 --> 00:30:22,510
Let's stop.

541
00:30:27,430 --> 00:30:28,150
Wait...

542
00:30:28,910 --> 00:30:29,430
Where's it?

543
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:31,100
Meat.

544
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:32,030
Take a rest.

545
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:39,830
He,

546
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,470
you're getting stronger these days.

547
00:30:41,950 --> 00:30:42,670
He was skilled.

548
00:30:43,150 --> 00:30:44,190
Now, he trains every day.

549
00:30:44,830 --> 00:30:46,110
He naturally keeps improving.

550
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:49,350
But sustaining this long-term,

551
00:30:49,670 --> 00:30:50,830
how can his body endure it?

552
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:55,910
Commander, Mr. Shen.

553
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:57,180
Commander.

554
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,070
Commander.

555
00:30:59,070 --> 00:30:59,590
Make way.

556
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:03,650
Make way.

557
00:31:05,150 --> 00:31:05,950
Focus on training.

558
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:31,250
笙ｪLight shines upon my heart笙ｪ

559
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:35,280
笙ｪUnveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream笙ｪ

560
00:31:35,450 --> 00:31:37,400
笙ｪThe resonance of courage
rings loud and clear笙ｪ

561
00:31:37,490 --> 00:31:42,420
笙ｪIt's the boldness
that defines existence笙ｪ

562
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:55,920
笙ｪI've seen the mountains笙ｪ

563
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,540
笙ｪAnd trodden through ice笙ｪ

564
00:31:57,800 --> 00:32:00,620
笙ｪDay after day, I venture alone笙ｪ

565
00:32:00,930 --> 00:32:02,320
笙ｪDestiny is my creed笙ｪ

566
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,780
笙ｪIdeals surge beneath the surface笙ｪ

567
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,720
笙ｪIgniting the flame against the winds笙ｪ

568
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,390
笙ｪA restless yearning in my soul笙ｪ

569
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:09,850
笙ｪGazing through the mire笙ｪ

570
00:32:10,020 --> 00:32:12,420
笙ｪWho cares about this boundless void笙ｪ

571
00:32:12,610 --> 00:32:14,660
笙ｪCharge ahead with blazing fervor笙ｪ

572
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:17,630
笙ｪStubbornly fighting with my life笙ｪ

573
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:22,510
笙ｪSoaring across the world's expanse笙ｪ

574
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:25,260
笙ｪThere must always be a longing笙ｪ

575
00:32:25,710 --> 00:32:30,780
笙ｪDisregard the wounds to seek the light笙ｪ

576
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,120
笙ｪLight shines upon my heart笙ｪ

577
00:32:33,430 --> 00:32:37,080
笙ｪUnveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream笙ｪ

578
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:39,210
